author: BBC
title: Romanian protesters light up huge rally with phone torches
text:
Up to 500,000 protesters shone torches on their phones at an anti-corruption rally in the capital Bucharest, lighting up Victory Square.
The demonstration came despite the government revoking a controversial decree which would have shielded many politicians from prosecution for corruption.
